---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---
<!-- Value Proposition -->
<section class="border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0e0e10]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl">Run Dojo. Keep your financial metadata off the surveillance web.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-300">
        Designed for Samourai Wallet, Dojo is the open‑source, self‑hosted backend that puts privacy and sovereignty first.
      </p>
    </div>
    <dl class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100">Hardened privacy defaults</dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Minimize data exposure with a backend built for private use.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100">Own your infrastructure</dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Self‑host at home or on your server. No third‑party trust required.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100">Simple to deploy</dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Follow our step‑by‑step install guides and get running quickly.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
        <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100">Ecosystem ready</dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">Integrates with protocols and libs including BIP47, Auth47, and more.</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
    <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
      <a href="/docs/install/download-and-verify" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-[#ed3b26] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0b0b0c] ring-1 ring-inset ring-[#ed3b26]/60 hover:bg-[#f24b38]">
        Start the install
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
